                <note rend="inline" type="source">814.51/312: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Thurston</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-12-19T21:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 19, 1919, 9 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received December 20, 3.55 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s December 9, 6 p.m. President Cabrera yesterday afternoon stated that
                    the Department of State is to use Professor Kemmerer’s report in the manner it
                    desires.</p>
                <pb facs="0372" n="287" xml:id="pg_287"/>
                <p>President Cabrera stated in connection with other points of Department’s
                    instruction just referred to that he was finding it difficult to choose suitable
                    delegates to the Financial Conference, but that when the committee was organized
                    it would be furnished comprehensive program for its guidance at conference.</p>
                <p>According to a reliable informant the President’s translator Delfino Sanchez
                    Latour has recently completed translation of Kemmerer report, but not even the
                    Minister of Finance has seen it.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Thurston</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
